title: What We Learned From the Combine
description:
Kevin, Nora, Kaelen, and Steven open up by discussing what they have seen and heard at the NFL combine. Then they talk about Kirk Cousins, Kyler Murray, Carson Wentz, and what the offseason could mean for them.

Host: Kevin Clark, Nora Princiotti, Steven Ruiz, and Kaelen Jones
Associate Producer: Stefan Anderson
Additional Production Supervision: Arjuna Ramgopal
